  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Museum of Peace in the city of Campinas, Brazil</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The following workplan refers to the UNESCO technical input and advice (SHS) to the future creation of the Museum of Peace and the Centre of Afro-Brazilian Education, Memory and Culture in the city of Campinas, Brazil.

This workplan is funded through an additional appropriation to the regular programme (AA) made possible through a donation of a company based in Campinas (Garret Motion). The funds donated to UNESCO will support the recruitment of the consultants who will provide the executive plans and the museum&apos;s collection (mainly oral reports from local communities).</narrative>
  </description>
